com.jdbwc.core.util

Class MySQLTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jdbwc.core.util.MySQLTypes

  • public final class MySQLTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    MySql types

    This deals with convering MySQL types to different forms. Most input for type requests come from a MySQL type id (integer).
    Version:
    2008-05-29, 2010-05-09
    Author:
    Tim Gall (Oz-DevWorX)
